<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1041539562"><cite class="citation wikicite" id="CITEREFLeon-Portilla2007"><a href="/wiki/Miguel_Leon-Portilla" class="mw-redirect" title="Miguel Leon-Portilla">Leon-Portilla, Miguel</a>. 2007. "La música de los aztecas / Music Among Aztecs", <i>Pauta</i>, no. 103:7–19.</cite></li>
<li><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1041539562"><cite class="citation wikicite" id="CITEREFLevitin2006">Levitin, Daniel J. 2006. <i><a href="/wiki/This_Is_Your_Brain_on_Music" title="This Is Your Brain on Music">This Is Your Brain on Music: The Science of a Human Obsession</a></i>. New York: Dutton. <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-525-94969-0" title="Special:BookSources/0-525-94969-0">0-525-94969-0</a>.</cite></li>
